{"tid":586480,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"男子小西灣邨墮樓亡","createTime":"2018-03-09T14:12:18.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-09T14:45:37.000Z","uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"8672c090de1bc7a14c3f4a94d3cfb988ae573aaa","tid":586480,"uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-09T14:12:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180309/large/1520599305_a86b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180309%2Flarge%2F1520599305_a86b.jpg&h=f96ebb30&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n墮樓男子倒卧簷蓬死亡。(溫文學攝)<br />\n<br />\n晚上7時許，一名年約70歲男子在小西灣邨瑞福樓墮樓，倒卧大廈簷蓬。救護員到場證實事主死亡，警員調查後，相信他由大廈走廊墮下，疑他因病厭世而輕生。<br />\n<br />\n24小時求助熱線︰<br />\n香港撒瑪利亞防止自殺會熱線︰23892222<br />\n撒瑪利亞會熱線(多種語言)︰28960000<br />\n生命熱線︰23820000<br />\n東華三院芷若園熱線︰18281<br />\n社會福利署熱線︰23432255<br />\n醫院管理局精神健康專線(24小時精神健康熱線諮詢服務)：24667350<br />\n明愛向晴熱線：18288<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20180309/57926025\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180309%2F57926025&d=cPUuASb54NjB%2BpfASYGOkdtKgwQIhJBw7VlnLihElrQ%3D&h=e6189941\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180309%2F57926025&h=4acdb00a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20180309/57926025</a>"},{"pid":"ac27f44f05f7c6e7df52c4328a883388fe65d3c3","tid":586480,"uid":41508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-09T14:14:18.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"81fcda5dda6991b4f4fd81a01c7a828a8bf3b6c2","tid":586480,"uid":53105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-09T14:45:37.000Z","msg":"政府幾時先搞安樂死，係咪要壓到無辜嘅人先做野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}